WEBVTT

00:10.411 --> 00:11.543
It's bad.

00:11.545 --> 00:13.545
He can physically harm people.

00:14.815 --> 00:16.047
I think
it wants to hurt me.

00:16.050 --> 00:19.051
I have been scratched
on my arms recently.

00:21.121 --> 00:22.621
He caused many deaths.

00:22.623 --> 00:25.991
I think it wants to kill
whoever's just living here.

00:27.128 --> 00:29.762
Do you think this thing
killed Wayla's father?

00:31.365 --> 00:32.965
And he's laughing.

00:32.967 --> 00:35.801
And he's saying, "Ha-ha-ha.
Kind of sucks, doesn't it?"

00:37.772 --> 00:39.905
Panic, panic, panic.

00:39.907 --> 00:42.607
My name is Amy Allen.

00:42.609 --> 00:44.476
I'm seeing, like, blood.

00:44.478 --> 00:46.311
The house just feels bad.

00:46.313 --> 00:49.047
I see dead people.

00:49.049 --> 00:53.519
This man is completely insane.

00:53.521 --> 00:55.287
I speak to dead people...

00:56.490 --> 00:58.791
Okay she doesn't
like it in there.

00:58.793 --> 01:00.692
...and they speak to me.

01:00.694 --> 01:02.694
He likes to
twist that knife.

01:02.696 --> 01:06.231
But there's only one way to
know if my findings are real.

01:06.233 --> 01:09.901
Something paranormal
is trying to kill them.

01:09.903 --> 01:11.403
I rely on my partner.

01:11.405 --> 01:12.771
I'm Steve Di Schiavi.

01:12.773 --> 01:14.840
I'm a retired New York City
homicide detective.

01:14.842 --> 01:16.908
Now, does he die
right there on the spot?

01:16.910 --> 01:20.813
I know every person,
every house has secrets.

01:20.815 --> 01:23.415
I think it's trying
to steal my soul.

01:23.417 --> 01:24.883
It's my job to reveal them.

01:24.885 --> 01:27.419
You ever get touched
like that again?

01:27.421 --> 01:29.221
But Steve and I never speak...

01:29.223 --> 01:31.323
We never communicate
during an investigation.

01:31.325 --> 01:32.824
...until the very end...

01:32.826 --> 01:34.292
I'm as stunned
as you guys are.

01:34.294 --> 01:36.962
...when we uncover
if it's safe for you to stay...

01:36.964 --> 01:38.830
I don't want anything to
happen to my daughter.

01:38.832 --> 01:40.933
...or time to get out.

01:40.935 --> 01:43.035
His goal is to kill you guys.

