I'm in Bogalusa, Louisiana.

01:58.752 --> 02:00.785
It's about an hour
north of New Orleans.

02:00.787 --> 02:02.520
I got a call
from a woman named Wayla.

02:02.522 --> 02:05.991
Now, she thinks the dead in
her home killed her father.

02:05.993 --> 02:07.926
And if Amy and I can't find
a way to get rid of him,

02:07.928 --> 02:09.928
she thinks she's gonna be next.

02:12.266 --> 02:13.465
Before Amy arrives,

02:13.467 --> 02:15.834
I clear the area
of any leading information.

02:17.604 --> 02:19.671
This house has a lot
of family photographs

02:19.673 --> 02:20.739
and religious symbols,

02:20.741 --> 02:22.674
so it's important
that I remove them all.

02:23.944 --> 02:26.011
When I'm done, the
location will be ready

02:26.013 --> 02:27.346
for tonight's walk.

02:37.925 --> 02:41.526
The energy here is
always in motion.

02:45.966 --> 02:48.066
We can't be calm here.

02:49.102 --> 02:52.237
Lots of anxiety.
The stress, the anxiety.

02:52.239 --> 02:56.140
The dead, they say all
of these living people

02:56.142 --> 02:58.777
are the real problem here.

03:05.118 --> 03:06.518
So, Wayla,
I'm glad I'm here now.

03:06.520 --> 03:08.854
When we spoke on the phone,
you sounded pretty terrified.

03:08.856 --> 03:10.254
What's going on?

03:10.256 --> 03:13.592
The paranormal activity here
is out of control.

03:13.594 --> 03:16.127
Day to day life here
is a living hell.

03:16.129 --> 03:19.331
I'm scared for my family.
I'm scared for myself.

03:19.333 --> 03:22.266
I called you
because we need help.

03:22.268 --> 03:24.102
You seem like you're
scared right now.

03:24.104 --> 03:26.471
I mean I'm better
now that you're here.

03:26.473 --> 03:27.673
Okay.

03:27.675 --> 03:28.840
Who all lives in
the house with you?

03:28.842 --> 03:31.610
My husband, Hector,
my son, Kristian, and me.

03:33.280 --> 03:34.279
All right, so what type
of experiences

03:34.281 --> 03:35.547
are we talking about?

03:35.549 --> 03:39.217
Well, we're having everything
from banging noises

03:39.219 --> 03:40.852
to disembodies voices.

03:41.822 --> 03:43.955
We see black shadows...

03:43.957 --> 03:44.756
Okay.

03:44.758 --> 03:46.024
...and physical violence.

03:46.026 --> 03:48.827
I am suffering health issues.

03:48.829 --> 03:50.495
What kind of health issues
are we talking about?

03:50.497 --> 03:54.800
I am having debilitating
stomach pains,

03:54.802 --> 03:58.103
and my dad was having
these same type of pains

03:58.105 --> 03:59.638
right before he died.

03:59.640 --> 04:01.707
Okay, so when did
your father live here?

04:01.709 --> 04:05.711
He lived here from 1996
until his death in 2008.

04:05.713 --> 04:07.245
He died here in the home.

04:07.247 --> 04:09.081
His bedroom was
right over there,

04:09.083 --> 04:12.684
that first room right there,
and it's now my son's bedroom.

04:12.686 --> 04:14.119
How old was Dad?

04:14.121 --> 04:14.853
79.

04:14.855 --> 04:16.120
So, what makes you think

04:16.123 --> 04:18.190
his death was caused
by the paranormal?

04:18.192 --> 04:19.958
A few days before he died,

04:19.959 --> 04:22.728
he had been speaking
with some friends of his...
Okay.

04:22.730 --> 04:25.664
...and he told them that he was
seeing things in the house.

04:25.666 --> 04:27.499
So what do you think
happened?

04:27.501 --> 04:30.469
I think maybe this house
has something to do with it...
Okay.

04:30.471 --> 04:35.674
...and I think that it might
be coming after me, too.

04:35.676 --> 04:37.809
Why don't you just move?

04:37.811 --> 04:39.410
I can't afford it.

04:39.412 --> 04:43.681
Between your father passing and
the hell you're living through,

04:43.683 --> 04:45.583
how are you dealing
with all of this?

04:45.585 --> 04:46.885
Not very well.

04:46.887 --> 04:53.025
I'm constantly stressed
and totally scared all the time.

04:53.027 --> 04:54.626
It's not living.

04:57.364 --> 05:00.832
I'm seeing this thing that looks
like a shadowy stick figure.

05:00.834 --> 05:05.871
Super tall, super slender,
long arms, long legs.

05:07.040 --> 05:09.708
Not really much
of a torso area.

05:09.710 --> 05:11.209
They're seeing it there.

05:14.247 --> 05:15.780
And it hates.

05:15.782 --> 05:17.315
It hates.

05:17.317 --> 05:19.918
They feel this, they feel
it in their stomachs.

05:20.987 --> 05:22.253
They're scared.

05:29.730 --> 05:32.731
I think this thing
killed somebody here.

05:36.369 --> 05:37.235
It's a male.

05:38.272 --> 05:39.471
Already sick.

05:40.741 --> 05:45.010
I see this thing put its --
inside their mouth

05:45.012 --> 05:47.579
and into their throat.

05:47.581 --> 05:51.749
Then I see this person just,
like, shrivel up into dust.

05:58.492 --> 05:59.958
What's going on in here?

05:59.960 --> 06:03.395
There has been
a female apparition

06:03.397 --> 06:05.964
right here in front
of my son's door.

06:05.966 --> 06:07.466
Can you describe her
for me?

06:07.468 --> 06:10.568
50s, kind of
sandy blonde hair.

06:10.570 --> 06:11.670
See-through.

06:11.672 --> 06:12.870
Anything else?

06:12.872 --> 06:15.840
We see black shadows
here all the time.

06:15.842 --> 06:21.379
I've seen a black mist come up,
like, out of the floor.
Okay.

06:21.381 --> 06:25.917
And it just formed up
into a human shape.

06:25.919 --> 06:27.152
Any kind of mechanical
stuff down there?

06:27.154 --> 06:29.120
No. There's nothing
in that area

06:29.122 --> 06:31.923
that could have caused
black smoke to come up.

06:31.925 --> 06:33.658
So, I mean,
with all this going on,

06:33.660 --> 06:34.893
what do you think it is?

06:34.895 --> 06:37.362
These black shadows
are extremely scary.

06:37.364 --> 06:38.196
Maybe demonic.

06:41.701 --> 06:42.901
This person's freaking out

06:42.903 --> 06:45.904
because of this shadow
stick-figure thing.

06:45.906 --> 06:48.006
This thing is old.

06:48.008 --> 06:49.541
And it's angry.

06:49.543 --> 06:52.944
And it has a lot
of personalities.

06:55.549 --> 06:58.016
This thing is fully conscious.

06:58.018 --> 07:01.286
But it's made up of people.

07:01.288 --> 07:02.287
How?

07:02.289 --> 07:04.756
It's a PK manifestation.

07:04.758 --> 07:07.759
From a long, long time ago.

07:07.761 --> 07:10.996
A PK manifestation
develops from a poltergeist

07:10.998 --> 07:13.498
with consistent exposure
to living agents,

07:13.500 --> 07:17.569
suffering extreme stress,
trauma, and emotional upheaval.

07:17.571 --> 07:20.839
They're extremely powerful
and can physically interact

07:20.841 --> 07:22.507
with their environment.

07:22.509 --> 07:24.910
So there are some, like,
living people here

07:24.912 --> 07:28.312
who had a lot of anger
and hatred.

07:28.314 --> 07:30.182
They created this.

07:30.184 --> 07:33.585
Feels like it comes and goes
through this closet here.

07:35.122 --> 07:36.855
It comes out of here.

07:36.857 --> 07:39.858
It comes out of here,
but it goes up...

07:43.130 --> 07:44.963
...when it hides.

07:51.605 --> 07:52.803
What's going on?

07:52.805 --> 07:55.406
Well, one of the
biggest issues in here

07:55.408 --> 07:57.575
is my closet door.

07:57.577 --> 08:01.313
The door knob will turn,
and it'll open on its own.

08:04.751 --> 08:05.950
I mean,
these are old doors,

08:05.952 --> 08:07.685
I don't know
how paranormal that is.

08:07.687 --> 08:10.288
We've had some issues

08:10.290 --> 08:12.824
with seeing things
come out of the closet, too.

08:12.826 --> 08:13.792
Like what?

08:13.794 --> 08:15.126
Black shadows,
things like that.

08:16.430 --> 08:18.363
That's a different story,
then.

08:18.365 --> 08:20.865
I'm terrified
of that closet.

08:20.867 --> 08:22.100
So anything else?

08:22.102 --> 08:25.971
I have mood swings
that range anywhere

08:25.973 --> 08:28.506
from anger
to depression,

08:28.508 --> 08:31.376
anxiety, stress, fear,

08:31.378 --> 08:33.912
might just fly off
the handle for no reason.

08:33.914 --> 08:37.448
Okay, so you think that's all
to do with the paranormal?

08:37.451 --> 08:38.783
Or do you think it has
something to do with the fact

08:38.784 --> 08:40.585
you're under the stress
from the paranormal?

08:40.587 --> 08:43.520
I think that whatever
is in this house

08:43.523 --> 08:45.056
is influencing a lot.

08:45.058 --> 08:46.691
And they're also affecting
my son, Kristian.

08:46.693 --> 08:50.795
His mood has even
turned strange and dark.

08:50.797 --> 08:52.530
Okay, in what way?

08:52.532 --> 08:55.266
He's obsessed with death.

08:55.268 --> 08:56.434
He likes to scare me.

08:57.704 --> 08:59.170
We have fought
so many times.

08:59.172 --> 09:02.007
So it's not just
the paranormal problem,

09:02.009 --> 09:03.341
it's tearing
your family apart.

09:03.343 --> 09:04.609
Absolutely.

09:04.611 --> 09:05.743
Anything else?

09:05.745 --> 09:08.546
Yeah, actually
I have been scratched

09:08.548 --> 09:11.883
in multiple places
on my body.

09:11.885 --> 09:13.951
This is my chest.

09:13.953 --> 09:16.888
It feels like
a never-ending burn,

09:16.890 --> 09:18.289
like a frozen burn.

09:18.291 --> 09:20.425
I know you got a cat here
somewhere, right?

09:20.427 --> 09:21.659
Yes, I do have a cat.

09:21.661 --> 09:23.228
That is not
a cat scratch.

09:23.230 --> 09:25.230
Whatever's here, what do you
think it wants from you?

09:25.232 --> 09:26.664
I think it wants
to hurt me.

09:26.666 --> 09:28.766
But I can't do it
anymore.

09:28.768 --> 09:30.034
I can't.

09:30.036 --> 09:33.571
All I want is a happy,
healthy, normal life.

09:36.843 --> 09:38.710
I think
this shadow thing attacks.

09:38.712 --> 09:41.513
I see it fighting
with somebody on here.

09:41.515 --> 09:45.817
A person is trying to sleep.

09:47.354 --> 09:51.156
And this thing is, like,
right here on the collar bones.

09:53.927 --> 09:56.561
It definitely attacks
people where they're weak,

09:56.563 --> 10:01.466
it makes them sick from that,
and it brings out regret

10:01.468 --> 10:04.202
and it brings out hatred.

10:04.204 --> 10:06.404
It wants to kill living people.

10:28.862 --> 10:30.662
Well Hector, I was talking
to your wife, Wayla

10:30.664 --> 10:32.530
and she was saying that
whatever's in this house

10:32.532 --> 10:34.899
is dangerous to you
and your family?

10:34.901 --> 10:37.135
Have you ever experienced
anything you can't explain?

10:42.009 --> 10:45.210
Does the voice say anything
to you in particular?

10:47.414 --> 10:48.713
Anything else happen?

11:08.568 --> 11:11.436
These moods swings, are they
affecting your relationship?

11:21.014 --> 11:23.448
So, Hector, do you think
that whatever's in this house

11:23.450 --> 11:24.949
is dangerous to you
and your family?

11:32.893 --> 11:34.992
I'm seeing an old woman.

11:34.994 --> 11:36.527
She's dead.

11:36.529 --> 11:42.433
This angry, or rather
hate-filled woman cries a lot.

11:42.435 --> 11:45.336
So I think that the
living actually would hear

11:45.338 --> 11:50.642
a female crying and maybe hear
a female talking to herself.

11:50.644 --> 11:54.813
So she's an extremely
negative person.

11:55.949 --> 11:59.984
So they might feel negative
and ugly.

12:04.290 --> 12:08.493
The old woman comes in here,
and she's angry.

12:11.297 --> 12:13.431
She wants to hurt, physically.

12:14.968 --> 12:18.269
Anybody that comes in here,
it wants to hurt.

12:18.271 --> 12:20.105
It's bad.

12:28.581 --> 12:31.315
Monica, I understand
you're good friends with Wayla.
Yes.

12:31.317 --> 12:32.616
How long you guys
known each other?

12:32.618 --> 12:34.352
- About 10 years.
- Okay.

12:34.354 --> 12:37.055
I moved here for three months
to help Wayla.

12:37.057 --> 12:39.057
Did you ever experience
anything you couldn't explain?

12:39.059 --> 12:42.393
I seen what looked
like the Grim Reaper.

12:42.395 --> 12:43.928
Guy with the hood with
the sickle and all that?

12:43.930 --> 12:46.264
Yes, just looked at me
and stared at me

12:46.266 --> 12:48.533
with the black-pitch eyes.

12:48.535 --> 12:49.601
What do you think it was?

12:49.603 --> 12:51.669
It was not human.

12:51.671 --> 12:53.604
It was demonic.

12:53.606 --> 12:54.972
Okay, so anything else?

12:54.974 --> 12:58.009
I've been physically
attacked, several times.

12:58.011 --> 13:00.411
I was scratched on my arm,

13:00.413 --> 13:03.214
I was shoved
on my right shoulder

13:03.216 --> 13:06.384
and I had been slapped
on the bottom of the leg.

13:06.386 --> 13:09.487
I get scared to death
being here.

13:09.489 --> 13:11.689
Wayla's pretty convinced
that whatever's in this house

13:11.691 --> 13:13.891
may have killed her father,
and now it's going after her.

13:13.893 --> 13:15.960
Do you agree with that?
- Yes I do.

13:15.962 --> 13:18.830
Absolutely believe 100%.

13:18.832 --> 13:22.000
I think it wants to kill
whoever's just living here.

13:22.002 --> 13:23.501
Okay.

13:30.710 --> 13:33.311
There's one male
who stays here all the time.

13:33.313 --> 13:36.047
He's sitting down.
He's wearing a suit.

13:36.049 --> 13:39.317
He's old.
He makes me feel sick.

13:40.954 --> 13:42.386
And he's laughing.

13:42.388 --> 13:45.490
And he's saying, "Ha-ha-ha.
Kind of sucks, doesn't it?"

13:47.493 --> 13:51.562
I think he can physically
harm people, and he does.

13:54.000 --> 13:57.568
And what kind of
physical stuff would he do?

13:57.570 --> 13:59.971
He says anything that
his heart desires.

14:01.140 --> 14:03.408
The children are
being strangled.

14:11.051 --> 14:12.784
So, Kristian,
how old are you?

14:12.786 --> 14:13.884
I'm 15.

14:13.886 --> 14:15.286
15, okay.

14:15.288 --> 14:16.788
So, I was talking
to Mom earlier,

14:16.790 --> 14:18.389
and she was saying
how she feels

14:18.391 --> 14:21.158
it's dangerous
in this house for you guys.
Yes.

14:21.160 --> 14:24.262
I understand you guys have
been physically attacked.

14:24.264 --> 14:27.431
I have been scratched
on my arms recently.

14:27.433 --> 14:29.166
- Okay.
- Here's a photo.

14:33.172 --> 14:34.839
All right, did you feel
anything scratch you?

14:34.841 --> 14:36.707
I didn't feel
a single thing.

14:36.709 --> 14:37.976
Okay, anything else?

14:37.978 --> 14:40.511
I was sitting in the room
watching TV.

14:40.513 --> 14:44.482
I looked over
and I saw a man in black

14:44.484 --> 14:47.352
walking around
my mom's bedroom.

14:47.354 --> 14:49.253
I immediately went
into my mom's room

14:49.255 --> 14:51.455
and I asked,
"Mama who's up in here?"

14:51.457 --> 14:53.124
And she said, "Nobody."

14:54.660 --> 14:56.461
Your mom tells me
you're scaring her

14:56.463 --> 14:57.929
and giving her
a hard time.

14:57.931 --> 14:59.030
What's up with that?

14:59.032 --> 15:00.898
It was just for
a harmless little prank.

15:00.900 --> 15:02.333
You should stop doing it,
though,

15:02.335 --> 15:03.935
'cause your mom doesn't need
the aggravation.

15:03.937 --> 15:05.469
She's got enough
on her mind.

15:05.471 --> 15:07.538
She doesn't want anything bad
to happen to you.

15:07.540 --> 15:09.807
Okay?
Appreciate that.

15:09.809 --> 15:10.808
Okay.

15:14.146 --> 15:17.482
This old man, he makes
living people delusional.

15:17.484 --> 15:20.985
I think he can manipulate them
and their emotions.

15:22.254 --> 15:25.990
I think that he
can influence them.

15:25.992 --> 15:30.861
Now it says, "Shh, shh, you're
giving all my secrets away."

15:36.702 --> 15:41.238
A lot of the directed, I think
to this, whoever this is.

15:41.240 --> 15:44.876
I think that the old man
can jump this person.

15:47.447 --> 15:51.382
He's saying something
about taking over a boy.

15:51.384 --> 15:54.151
He's a very sick person --
very sick.

16:08.517 --> 16:11.252
So I made my usual calls,
and get this.

16:11.254 --> 16:13.054
One of the historians
I reached out to

16:13.056 --> 16:15.656
is actually a descendant
of one of the first owners

16:15.658 --> 16:16.957
of Wayla's property.

16:16.959 --> 16:19.460
Turns out his family was
involved in a brutal homicide

16:19.462 --> 16:20.695
back in the 1890s.

16:20.697 --> 16:21.862
I'm heading over
to meet this guy

16:21.864 --> 16:23.798
and find out
exactly what happened.

16:29.372 --> 16:31.371
So, Bill, I appreciate
you meeting with me.

16:31.373 --> 16:34.074
Now, I know you were a
relative of the Williams family

16:34.076 --> 16:36.377
that actually owned my
client's property at one time.

16:36.379 --> 16:37.979
What can you tell me
about them?

16:37.981 --> 16:41.682
Your client's property was
owned by Martin Williams,

16:41.684 --> 16:45.686
but in my family we grew up
knowing him as Captain Martin.

16:45.688 --> 16:48.522
Captain, where'd he get from?
The army or something?

16:48.524 --> 16:52.126
Yes, he served as a Captain
in the Confederate Army.

16:52.128 --> 16:53.361
There's a photograph.

16:53.363 --> 16:55.997
He was in many battles,
and he eventually

16:55.999 --> 16:59.800
made his way back
to Bogalusa in 1865.

16:59.802 --> 17:01.235
What's the story
with this homicide?

17:01.237 --> 17:06.973
Well, in November 1894,
his son A.C. Williams

17:06.976 --> 17:10.411
got in a argument with another
gentleman, Chris Morris.

17:10.413 --> 17:12.378
Now, instead of picking
a fight with Morris,

17:12.381 --> 17:14.013
he just went home
and told his father.

17:14.016 --> 17:15.182
All right,
so how old was A.C.?

17:15.184 --> 17:16.050
28 years old.

