a cooperative endeavor

20:13.162 --> 20:14.694
with white laborers,

20:14.696 --> 20:16.697
which is almost unprecedented
in southern history.

20:16.699 --> 20:19.566
I mean this had to piss off the
powers that be and the bosses.

20:19.568 --> 20:21.501
They go bananas
about this.

20:21.503 --> 20:24.705
And so they create
the special police force

20:24.707 --> 20:27.307
to smash this
unionization attempt.

20:27.309 --> 20:28.109
So what do they do?

20:28.111 --> 20:29.710
First target is Sol Dacus.

20:29.712 --> 20:31.011
Okay.

20:31.013 --> 20:33.914
So this is
November 21, 1919.

20:33.916 --> 20:36.884
Some say as many as 100
