20:48.564 --> 20:50.531
And what they're gonna do,
is they're gonna send

20:50.533 --> 20:54.267
two white union organizers
with Sol Dacus

20:54.269 --> 20:56.337
and they're gonna
walk up and down

20:56.339 --> 20:57.772
the main street
of Bogalusa.

20:57.774 --> 21:01.142
