21:06.415 --> 21:07.581
from my client's
property?

21:07.583 --> 21:08.682
About 3,000 feet.

21:08.684 --> 21:09.750
Okay,
so it's pretty close.

21:09.752 --> 21:10.951
Very close.

21:10.953 --> 21:12.285
I'm sure management
got word of this,

21:12.287 --> 21:15.089
