21:15.091 --> 21:18.359
In the end, it turns into
a full pitched battle.

21:18.361 --> 21:20.695
Dozens and dozens
of shots are fired.

21:20.697 --> 21:21.762
What's the body count?

21:21.764 --> 21:23.297
Once the hail of bullets
stopped,

21:23.299 --> 21:26.633
you've got three white union
organizers killed outright.

21:26.635 --> 21:29.937
A fourth one will die
