Mamie and Will live in
Old Main Street in Bogalusa.

23:34.430 --> 23:37.198
Cola Lemming is living
next door.
Okay.

23:37.200 --> 23:41.301
January of 1949, Cola Lemming
invites Ms. Furr over

23:41.303 --> 23:45.139
for a cup of coffee that turns
