23:45.141 --> 23:46.807
Okay, what happened?

23:46.809 --> 23:48.542
Almost immediately
upon returning

23:48.544 --> 23:51.945
to her house next door,
Ms. Furr was in such distress,

23:51.947 --> 23:53.480
