29:33.555 --> 29:35.688
It involved two women who
lived next door to each other,

29:35.690 --> 29:37.357
about a mile from here.

29:37.359 --> 29:39.025
In January of 1949,

29:39.027 --> 29:41.094
a 43-year-old woman
named Cola Lemming

29:41.096 --> 29:43.429
invited her next door
neighbor, Mamie Furr,

29:43.431 --> 29:44.898
