30:01.917 --> 30:03.784
It was a classic love triangle.

30:03.786 --> 30:06.452
Lemming was having an affair
with Furr's husband.

30:06.454 --> 30:09.856
I was able to get an article
after Lemming's arrest.

30:09.858 --> 30:12.526
Her photo kind of reminds
me of how you described her.

30:13.595 --> 30:16.797
She was convicted of the murder
and sentenced to life in prison.

30:18.267 --> 30:21.801
Now, somehow, she winds up
